Oscar GC
========

Oscar GC is a custom distribution of Goose (Apache-2.0). The repo is a
multi-license codebase: Oscar-authored work is licensed under
AGPL-3.0-or-later (see LICENSE); inherited and bundled work keeps its
original license. See LICENSES/README.md for the per-path map and
LICENSES/{Apache-2.0,MIT,MPL-2.0,Python-2.0}.txt for verbatim license
texts.

This NOTICE file enumerates every upstream attribution Oscar GC carries.

