Sprint 22 (ADR-075) lifted five MCPs from Lavern's `src/mcps/` and
adapted them into Oscar GC's in-tree bundle. Each MCP is Apache-2.0,
Copyright 2026 s-arturko (Oscar GC adapter), with the verbatim Lavern
source preserved under `src/_lavern-original/` for diff-against-upstream
review:

  oscar/mcps/baselines/           ← Lavern src/mcps/baselines.ts
  oscar/mcps/document-checks/     ← Lavern src/mcps/document-checks.ts
  oscar/mcps/document-reader/     ← Lavern src/mcps/document-reader.ts
